{
  "stem": "17135.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told you the story that the snow-- we had to fill up the the things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There we did it with sand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And who were the kapos?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All Poles.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Poles.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I, I, I said it in-- when, when I testified later in the Auschwitz trial-- one name was Oberkapo Bolek.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a rrrrr, beefy Pole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was such a murderer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He literally-- I was told-- got awards, was praised by SS for each person that he killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Every day they were literally competing with each other, the kapos, who, who is a better killer than the other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's what was going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And no mercy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No understanding.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were such anti-Semitic bastards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I could never believe-- to me, it was so hard to understand that a person that suffers from the Nazis and knows how beastialic, how, how, how, how inhuman they are, could do this with gusto.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "With gusto!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Not because he was forced.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He, he, he was-- he wanted to become oberkapo, muchas kapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Oberkapo is super kapo, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was the head of all the kapos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's was but the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then, we were assigned to work in the factory, together with civilians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were about 35,000 civilians that worked there-- Poles, forced labor from Yugoslavia, from all the occupied territories.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "For example, if one was a Pole, he had a P.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "If one was a Frenchman, he had a F, a sign.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There were Frenchman there, all kinds of people that were skilled laborers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, locksmiths, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] carpenters, mechanics, electricians, what have you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I-- look what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was cocky and, and, and sharp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After, after work we went to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We're eating.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
